videos.description: Arizona State guard Josh Christopher absorbs contact and double-clutches at the rim to convert a layup in traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (ASU's Christopher hangs in air for tough basket) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: ASU's Christopher hangs in air for tough basket

videos.description: Arizona State guard Remy Martin puts his defender on skates with a crossover and then finishes at the hoop with a scoop layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Remy Martin crosses defender for Sun Devils score) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Remy Martin crosses defender for Sun Devils score

videos.description: Arizona State freshman Marcus Bagley, younger brother of former Duke star Marvin Bagley, knocks down a pair of 3-pointers early in his first NCAA game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (ASU freshman Bagley drains pair of 3s early) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: ASU freshman Bagley drains pair of 3s early

videos.description: URI guard Fatts Russell gets into the lane and splits two defenders with a pass to Antwan Walker, who finishes through contact to score.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fatts Russell drops dime for URI and-1) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fatts Russell drops dime for URI and-1

videos.description: Malik Martin's jumper is off the mark, but Antwan Walker rises up for the emphatic putback slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Walker flushes putback dunk with authority for Rhode Island) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Walker flushes putback dunk with authority for Rhode Island

videos.description: Arizona State's Holland Woods picks Jeremy Sheppard's pocket and scores an easy layup in transition to put the game out of reach in the closing moments.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Woods steals and scores to seal ASU win over URI) 2020/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Woods steals and scores to seal ASU win over URI
